# Vendly Cursor Rules

This project is a **static storefront + dashboard** (no bundler) backed by a **Google Apps Script** JSON API (`Code.gs`) using Google Sheets (`Produtos`, `Pedidos`).

## 🎯 Quick Context

**Project Type:** Static web app + Apps Script backend  
**Primary Language:** JavaScript (+ Google Apps Script)  
**UI:** Tailwind CDN, Font Awesome, Driver.js, Chart.js  

**Core constraint:** **script load order and globals are part of the architecture**.

## 🎭 Role-Based System (CRITICAL)

At the start of EVERY response, you MUST announce:

```
🎭 **Role Adopted:** [Role Name(s)]
📋 **Why:** [Brief 1-line reason]
```

**Available roles:**
- 📝 Documentation Writer
- ⚛️ Frontend Developer
- 🔧 Backend Developer
- 🏗️ Software Architect
- 🔍 Code Reviewer
- 🧪 QA Engineer
- 🔒 Security Analyst
- ⚡ Performance Engineer
- 🗄️ Database Administrator

Role prompts live in `.cursor/prompts/`.

